{"word":"ἐπισκιάζω","slug":"ἐπισκιάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπισϰιάζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, σϰιάζω</el> ‘darken, overshadow’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σκιά\">σκιά</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> envelope, surround <a href='B:470 17:5'>Mt 17:5</a>; <a href='B:480 9:7'>Mk 9:7</a>; <a href='B:490 9:34'>Lk 9:34</a>.</b> In imagery of divine power <b><a href='B:490 1:35'>Lk 1:35</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a href='B:20 40:34'>Ex 40:34f</a>). <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> fall on,</b> of a shadow <b><a href='B:510 5:15'>Ac 5:15</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ lit.\">lit.</a> ‘shadow shadowed on’ someone)<b>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπισκηνόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπισκοπέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}